                             JERRY
               My house? You have to be on the lease 
               to press to buzzer. Yeah?
 
               
                             INTERCOM
               It's George.

               
                             JERRY
               Come on up.

               
                             ELAINE
               Casus belli.

               
                             JERRY
               What's that?

               
                             ELAINE
