                         THE PARKING GARAGE



                             Written by

                            Larry David




               
               INT. ESCALATOR - GOING DOWN TO A GARAGE.

               
                             IN SINGLE FILE
               GEORGE, JERRY and ELAINE, WHO'S CARRYING 
               A PLASTIC BAG WITH GOLDFISH, AND KRAMER 
               WHO'S HAVING A ROUGH TIME WITH A LARGE, 
