               but stay on Biscayne. Don't get off 
               Biscayne. You understand me?
 
               
                             JERRY
               Stay on Biscayne.

               
                             HELEN
               You're going underwater?

               
                             JERRY
               Yes. Generally that's where scuba diving 
               is done.
 
               
