               What do you have to go underwater for? 
               What's down there that's so special?
 
               
               
                             JERRY
               What's so special up here?

               
               (Elaine open the guest room's door and she's in pain)

               
                             ELAINE
               Oh!

               
               (everybody get up and walk to her)

               
                             HELEN
               What's the matter?

               
                             ELAINE
