               What did Blanche say?

               
                             EVELYN
               I don't know. She said Jerry wanted 
               the pen.
 
               
                             JERRY
               I never really wanted the pen.

               
                             MORTY
               He gave him the pen.

               
                             HELEN
               Morty.

               
                             EVELYN
